snippet.title: ADDICTED
snippet.description:
This channel presents both paid and free music:Minimal Techno, Progresive House, Melodic Techno, Techno and sometimes other.
I'm a Techno/Melodic Techno DJ
EVERY UPLOAD ON THIS CHANNEL (VIDEO , DJ SET , Mixing ) IS MADE EXCLUSIVELY BY ME .
The names of the artists are used only for the title, set is complied and mixed by ADDICTED ! 

it's an Youtube Channel showcasing a various styles of Electronic music like : Progressive music , minimal techno , melodic techno . i have license all the tracks . Proof of license available upon request. All my videos are free / paid or licensed .  Proof of license available upon request. Our mission is to find a great artists and promote them . I have big plans in future and if you want to join our community just tap the subscribe button !
